\n入境可以係關口屈尻你<br />\n海關可以係你行李擺走私屈尻你<br />\n懲教可以打柒你班政治犯而無人知"},{"pid":"3e7158e63f827158253633981b402fdc711438da","tid":1204090,"uid":234617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做呢份工 你開心咩 <br />\n你日日比人屌老母你對得住佢地咩</span><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/POcuGRW.png[/im]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOcuGRW.png%5B%2Fim%5D&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=5fb29167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/POcuGRW.png[/im]</a>"},{"pid":"cd5f63735527c369c7b091af2c17a3bfb7856831","tid":1204090,"uid":234617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3e7158e63f827158253633981b402fdc711438da","tid":1204090,"uid":234617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做呢份工 你開心咩 <br />\n你日日比人屌老母你對得住佢地咩</span><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/POcuGRW.png[/im]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOcuGRW.png%5B%2Fim%5D&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=5fb29167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/POcuGRW.png[/im]</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqbCQMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqbCQMe.png&h=9cf98f00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8369b6e6b573cc4e98b1b05f8a1e859a5d27daaa","tid":1204090,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"唔係重點，但阻阻大家，有緣見到CCTVB做直播/收音就大嗌或自製banner<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗌咩唔係重點，齊心屌鳩TVB<br />\n目的係影響tvb收音，拍攝緊嘅畫面<br />\n過往經驗，佢做live無得cut，直上電視，但新聞時段就會cut晒呢啲畫面/收音，令佢無嘢播都好<br />\n<br />\n橫掂TVB妓者都係鳩噏<br />\n血債血償，清鳩tvb袋<br />\n<br />\n有片，例子參考 : <br />\n[呼籲]有緣見到CCTVB，大家要識做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202083</a>"},{"pid":"bc01454c58fda2e9e63c52803dbc7b6d0d421bcd","tid":1204090,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"從來做卧底既效用先係最多<br />\n入警隊，可以捉少幾個學生，<br />\n見到有違禁品扮睇唔到放人，<br />\n要起義果陣，可以做leader帶隊兵出黎"},{"pid":"112b55a521cc3b900d659ba4c8b5c11e446bc8d3","tid":1204090,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"督察要求好高<br />\n係睇唔過睇班散仔<br />\n兩萬六死難仔"},{"pid":"3e95edfe89c52078bae27175565f66a379bb704e","tid":1204090,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"如果你哋覺得共產黨係可信嘅、你哋將會喺權力鬥爭之下成功生存到嘅，咪即管去考囉，只不過到時出事嘅話唔好嚟搵我。"},{"pid":"edae70129023a56ed73dfdb77da688505f5c1104","tid":1204090,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔洗旨意移民"},{"pid":"f2614f37137b9eb73930ad7232fd91a30794a2d8","tid":1204090,"uid":234617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112b55a521cc3b900d659ba4c8b5c11e446bc8d3","tid":1204090,"uid":229508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"督察要求好高<br />\n係睇唔過睇班散仔<br />\n兩萬六死難仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"要求係好高 <br />\n如果你咁叻入左去唔好埋沒左良心<br />\n你甘心做中國傀儡咩<br />\n唔甘心 但為傀儡又做到啲咩 你真係會反抗咩"},{"pid":"4d848b4dd3c559ca70838bdacf0690a3f2fc7d33","tid":1204090,"uid":38277,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"我做緊其他紀律部隊 officer rank<br />\n我都好L 憎d警察<br />\n但諗深一層，我唔係高尚過佢地好多<br />\n我自己都覺得好慚愧，一方面屌鳩個仆街政府。但另一方面自己幫政府打工<br />\n部門入面好多老屎忽或者高層，佢地可能係社會上既得利益者，好多都係盲撐政府<br />\n相反新一代入職既年青人，其實好多都有自己獨立思考<br />\n但礙於工作環境同階級觀念，佢地都唔敢係工作期間表態<br />\n可能會有人叫我辭職，sorry 我仲未有咁既勇氣<br />\n我只能夠聽日拎半日假出去野餐"},{"pid":"8b7c771775d7b1d2a0d67929bbdacc5ddd4a949d","tid":1204090,"uid":140769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10818f5beedff6ba1